Package: labormarket
Title: Tools for Learning How Labor Markets Work
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Hugo", "Sant'Anna", email = "hsantanna@uga.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of econometric tools made for the exploration of worker-firm matched datasets. It aims to simplify complex concepts, and serves as an invaluable ally for both undergraduates and graduates in navigating labor economics research.
